enwriter *[[1983]] &ndash; [[Mido (footballer)|Mido]], Egyptian footballer and sportscaster * 1983 &ndash; [[Aziz Ansari]], American comedian, actor, producer, and screenwriter * 1983 &ndash; [[Emily Blunt]], English actress *[[1986]] &ndash; [[Emerson Conceição]], Brazilian footballer * 1986 &ndash; [[Skylar Grey]], American singer-songwriter * 1986 &ndash; [[Kazuya Kamenashi]], Japanese singer-songwriter and actor * 1986 &ndash; [[Jerod Mayo]], American football player * 1986 &ndash; [[Ola Svensson]], Swedish singer-songwriter *[[1987]] &ndash; [[Ab-Soul]], American rapper * 1987 &ndash; [[Theophilus London]], Trinidadian-American singer-songwriter and producer * 1987 &ndash; [[Zak Kirkup]], Member of the [[Parliament of Western Australia]] *[[1988]] &ndash; [[Nicolás Gaitán]], Argentinian footballer *[[1989]] &ndash; [[Evan Bates]], American ice dancer *[[1989]] &ndash; [[Jérémy Pied]], French footballer *[[1990]] &ndash; [[Kevin Connauton]], Canadian ice hockey player * 1990 &ndash; [[Terry Hawkridge]], English footballer * 1990 &ndash; [[Marco Scandella]], Canadian ice hockey player *[[1992]] &ndash; [[Casemiro]], Brazilian footballer * 1992 &ndash; [[Kyriakos Papadopoulos]], Greek footballer *[[1993]] &ndash; [[Chris Grevsmuhl]], Australian rugby league player *[[1994]] &ndash; [[Dakota Fanning]], American actress *[[1995]] &ndash; [[Andrew Wiggins]], Canadian basketball player <!--Please do not add yourself, non-notable people, fictional characters, or people without Wikipedia articles to this list. No red links, please. Do not link multiple occurrences of the same year, just link the first occurrence. If there are multiple people in the same birth year, put them in alphabetical order. Do not trust "this year in history" websites for accurate date information.-->
