'''MakFest''' ({{lang-mk|МакФест}}) founded in 1986, is the largest festival of Macedonian popular music. It is held every year in November, in [[Štip]], [[Republic of Macedonia]], at the Cultural Center "Aco Šopov" ({{lang-mk|Дом на Културата "Ацо Шопов"}}). MakFest is a member of FIDOF (International Federation of Festival Organizations) with headquarters in Los Angeles, CA, USA. In 1997, MakFest was awarded the "Festival of The Year" distinction by [[FIDOF]]. <ref>{{cite web|author=Makfest, A.D.|publisher=MakFest A.D.|url=http://www.makfest.org/zamakfest.html|title=Za Makfest|date=2007-04-08|accessdate=2008-09-18}}</ref>
